      <title>中国下调关键贷款利率以支持经济增长</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-cuts-benchmark-loan-prime-rates-by-25-bps-2024-10-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[作为刺激经济的一揽子措施的一部分，中国上个月还下调了其他政策利率，并在周一的月度定价中一如预期地下调了基准贷款利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-cuts-benchmark-loan-prime-rates-by-25-bps-2024-10-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 01:12:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国银行将保证外汇汇率窗口延长至一年</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/bofa-extends-guaranteed-fx-rate-window-year-2024-10-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为了在跨货币交易量上升的情况下降低交易风险，美国银行周一将其保证汇率延长至一年，这是业内最长的期限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/bofa-extends-guaranteed-fx-rate-window-year-2024-10-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 01:03:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
